    <h1>Word-of-Mouth Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">The organic or amplified spread of brand recommendations from one person to another. Word-of-mouth marketing drives <strong>purchase decisions at higher rates than any paid channel</strong> because people trust people — and the conditions that produce it can be systematically engineered.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
